trans-unit.source: Provides a file system implementation of the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> class.
trans-unit.target: Gir en fil systemimplementering av <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>klasse.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The FileWebRequest class implements the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>`abstract` base class for Uniform Resource Identifiers (URIs) that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: FileWebRequest klassen implementerer <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> `abstract` basisklasse for Uniform Resource identifikatorene (URIer) som bruker den `file://` skjemaet til å be om lokale filer.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Do not use the <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Ikke bruk av <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to initialize new instances of the FileWebRequest class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode for å initialisere nye forekomster av klassen FileWebRequest.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the URI scheme is `file://`, the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A> method returns a FileWebRequest object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis URI-skjemaet er `file://`, <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A>metoden returnerer et FileWebRequest-objekt.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Create%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A> method makes a synchronous request for the file specified in the <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.RequestUri%2A> property and returns a <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse> object that contains the response.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>metoden foretar en synkron forespørsel for filen som er angitt i den <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.RequestUri%2A>egenskapen og returnerer et <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>objekt som inneholder svaret.</xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.RequestUri%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can make an asynchronous request for the file using the <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A> and <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Du kan gjøre en asynkron forespørsel for filen med det <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A>og <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you want to write data to a file, the <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A> method returns a <xref:System.IO.Stream> instance to write to.
trans-unit.target: Når du ønsker å skrive data til en fil av <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A>metoden returnerer en <xref:System.IO.Stream>forekomst til å skrive til.</xref:System.IO.Stream> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A> and <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A> methods provide asynchronous access to the write data stream.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A>og <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A>metoder gir asynkrone tilgang i dataflyten for skriving.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A>

trans-unit.source: The FileWebRequest class relies on the <xref:System.IO.File> class for error handling and code access security.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FileWebRequest avhengig av <xref:System.IO.File>klasse feilbehandling og kodetilgangssikkerhet.</xref:System.IO.File>

trans-unit.source: After a request is canceled, calling the <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A>, or <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A> method causes a <xref:System.Net.WebException> with the <xref:System.Net.WebException.Status%2A> property set to <xref:System.Net.WebExceptionStatus>.
trans-unit.target: Når en forespørsel er avbrutt, kaller den <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A>, <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A>, eller <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A>metoden fører til en <xref:System.Net.WebException>med <xref:System.Net.WebException.Status%2A>egenskapen satt til <xref:System.Net.WebExceptionStatus>.</xref:System.Net.WebExceptionStatus> </xref:System.Net.WebException.Status%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebException> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetRequestStream%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetRequestStream%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetRequestStream%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.EndGetResponse%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.BeginGetResponse%2A> </xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the length of time until the request times out.

trans-unit.source: A Domain Name System (DNS) query may take up to 15 seconds to return or time out.
trans-unit.target: En spørring (DNS-System) kan ta opptil 15 sekunder å returnere tidsavbrudd.

trans-unit.source: If your request contains a host name that requires resolution and you set Timeout to a value less than 15 seconds, it may take 15 seconds or more before a <xref:System.Net.WebException> is thrown to indicate a time-out on your request.
trans-unit.target: Hvis forespørselen inneholder et vertsnavn som krever løsning, og angi tidsavbrudd til en verdi mindre enn 15 sekunder, kan det ta 15 sekunder eller mer før en <xref:System.Net.WebException>er et for å angi et tidsavbrudd for forespørselen.</xref:System.Net.WebException>

trans-unit.source: The time, in milliseconds, until the request times out, or the value <xref:System.Threading.Timeout.Infinite?displayProperty=fullName> to indicate that the request does not time out.
trans-unit.target: Ønsket tid i millisekunder før forespørselen blir tidsavbrutt, eller verdien <xref:System.Threading.Timeout.Infinite?displayProperty=fullName> til å angi at forespørselen er tidsavbrutt.
